The paper deals with the problem of predicting knowledge unit relatedness in Stack Overflow, which is a technical community question-answering forum. This task involves analyzing the content of question threads and determining their degree of relatedness. This task is closely related to information retrieval (IR), natural language processing (NLP), machine learning (ML), and deep learning (DL). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.SI, and cs.DL.
